<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ذُو الرُّمَّةِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِلَى كُلِّ بَهْوٍ ذِي أَخٍ يَسْتَعِدُّهُ ... إِذَا هَجَّرَتْ أَيَّامُهُ لِلتَّحَوُّلِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يَقُولُ إِلَى جَانِبِهِ بَهْوٍ مِثْلِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>